sources.title: 09 Let's Get Tough
sources.description: Let's Get Tough!  is a 1942 film and the ninth film in the  East Side Kids  series, starring  Leo Gorcey  (as Muggs),  Huntz Hall  (as Glimpy),  Bobby Jordan  (as Danny), and  Robert Armstrong  (as "Pops" the Cop). Released in early 1942, it was directed by  Wallace Fox , and features the gang caught up in  World War II  and fighting the  Black Dragon Society , an enemy  sabotage  ring.
